{
  "stem": "3952.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- most of them were working in the harbor, you know taking off, loading off loads from ships, and et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was their professions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- by nature, they were strong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were people who worked physical work, so they were stronger people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And immediately they took over the-- the government to govern the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would-- they would be the ones who were over the latrines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Latrines were the toilets, you know, open latrines, the huge place where you-- 20 people would sit down in one shot-- sit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You wouldn't sit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You would stand, you just-- and do what you had to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would-- they would clean those latrines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But because of that, they wouldn't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would work in the camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they had access to food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had access to things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had the better place to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, they were kind of dominating the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The camp-- the tents, these Finnish tents were-- we had like, I think, 12 blocks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A line up the hill, like seven or eight or nine tents like this in a line, it was called one block.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And each block had a blockalteste who was the-- the overseer of the block, the responsible for the block, who was an inmate, a Jew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "These were mostly Polish people who were older in the camp already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were-- they were already-- their sufferings went on for like four years or so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they hated us, because when they were in trouble, they said, we still had-- had a good life in Hungaria, in Hungary, or wherever we were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they hated us.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
